{"tid":2510534,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚餐飯覺得我老細賤格得黎又講得幾啱......","createTime":"2021-04-30T08:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T08:41:10.000Z","uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0422e6f420acfcb0ca7444dd289f9313cdb22f","tid":2510534,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"尋晚跟老細同第二間公司食飯，對面有個女仔食開黃店（佢話佢食左兩年黃店），我老細就同佢講，如果佢肯食一啖美心就比一萬蚊佢，個女仔梗係唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我老細一路加上去，五萬蚊、十萬蚊、去到二十萬話係final offer，個女仔心動，同意食一啖美心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老細即場寫咗支票俾佢，同埋加多句：「你哋啲所謂食黃店抗爭嘅人都係最撚虛偽，喺錢面前你哋班垃圾咪一啲道德原則都冇。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a22d28aea24cd1121b107660104015bd857722c","tid":2510534,"uid":388757,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"洗撚廿萬咩<br />\n<br />\n比廿蚊佢話係家長飯票就仆左去食啦"},{"pid":"3adc613c0c3b79bcfd7bf1e63b01224f938b29d1","tid":2510534,"uid":11294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱見到想開post點知俾你開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a70cf0fd4f7d311f5609b6d48d2673d2637f04","tid":2510534,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a22d28aea24cd1121b107660104015bd857722c","tid":2510534,"uid":388757,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"洗撚廿萬咩<br />\n<br />\n比廿蚊佢話係家長飯票就仆左去食啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fc9d8441edd1b16a8ae1bbda72e61833fc702d","tid":2510534,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3adc613c0c3b79bcfd7bf1e63b01224f938b29d1","tid":2510534,"uid":11294,"like":1,"d